        "text": "Wash. D.C.\nDear Mr. Hoover!-\nSince reading so much\nabout flying saucers and other\nobjects in the sky, I have\ndecided to write you about a theory\nwhich I came to believe in 1917.\nOne evening about 10- I saw"
      },
